","kind":"theorem","line":473,"name":"List.IsRotated.dropLast_tail","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Data/List/Rotate.lean#L473-L480"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Data/List/Rotate.html#List.IsRotated.cons_getLast_dropLast\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">IsRotated</span>.<span class=\"name\">cons_getLast_dropLast</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">L</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hL</span> : <span class=\"fn\">L</span> <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Ne\">≠</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.nil\">[</a><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.nil\">]</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">L</span>.<a href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.getLast\">getLast</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">hL</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.cons\">::</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">L</span>.<a href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.dropLast\">dropLast</a></span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/List/Rotate.html#List.IsRotated\">~r</a> <span class=\"fn\">L</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Data/List/Rotate.html#List.IsRotated.cons_getLast_dropLast","kind":"theorem","line":464,"name":"List.IsRotated.cons_getLast_dropLast","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Data/List/Rotate